For complaints that cannot be resolved between BHRW and the complainant, BHRW agrees to participate in the following dispute resolution procedures to resolve disputes pursuant to the Safe Harbor Principles:

1. for disputes involving personal information received by BHRW from Switzerland, BHRW agrees to cooperate with the Swiss Federal Data Protection and Information Commissioner (FDPIC);

2. for disputes involving employment-related personal information received by BHRW from the EEA, BHRW agrees to cooperate with the data protection authorities in the EEA and to participate in the dispute resolution procedures of the panel established by the European data protection authorities (EU DPAs).
